text: Duck Duck Goose is a 2018 computer-animated comedy movie directed by Chris Jenkins. The movie was produced by Original Force Animation (USA) and Wanda Media Co., Ltd (China). It stars Jim Gaffigan, Zendaya, Lance Lim, Greg Proops, Natasha Leggero and Stephen Fry. It was released on March 9, 2018. == Cast == * Jim Gaffigan as Peng * Zendaya as Chi * Lance Lim as Chao * Greg Proops as Banzou * Natasha Leggero as Jinjing * Stephen Fry as Frazier * Craig Ferguson as Giles * Carl Reiner as Larry * Jennifer Grey as Edna * Diedrich Bader as Bing * Rick Overton as Stanley == References == == Other websites == * * * Can Open Road Nabs S.
